<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id79f09e6e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2002—<ref href="/us/pl/107/308">Pub. L. 107–308</ref> substituted “Western Hemisphere” for “western hemisphere”.</p>
